on my skateboard.

05:34.417 --> 05:36.208
So she's special, right?

05:36.208 --> 05:38.417
Oh, yeah.

05:38.417 --> 05:40.291
Yeah.

05:40.291 --> 05:41.834
You ever have something
really great come along

05:41.834 --> 05:43.417
