05:43.417 --> 05:44.458
Oh, yeah.

05:44.458 --> 05:46.083
Your brother Greg.

05:46.083 --> 05:47.917
Yeah, we were supposed
to stop at two,

05:47.917 --> 05:49.208
but it all worked out,

05:49.208 --> 05:51.625
because he's successful.

05:51.625 --> 05:52.750
Thanks, Dad.

05:52.750 --> 05:54.917
Can you please just help me
get the car started?

05:54.917 --> 05:57.125
Well, there is an old trick
I used to use

05:57.125 --> 05:59.583
when I couldn't get
an aging aircraft started.

05:59.583 --> 06:01.583
