06:03.458 --> 06:05.375
Little tequila.

06:05.375 --> 06:07.375
Try her now.

06:10.208 --> 06:11.333
(engine starting)

06:11.333 --> 06:14.333
-There you go. Ah?
-Hey!

06:14.333 --> 06:16.083
Wait, you put tequila
in a plane?

06:16.083 --> 06:17.250
Yes, sir.

06:17.250 --> 06:19.542
Works good on old motors.

06:19.542 --> 06:21.792
Also good in old pilots.

06:24.500 --> 06:26.625
