06:26.625 --> 06:27.959
Go get her, son.

06:27.959 --> 06:34.875
♪

06:40.625 --> 06:41.750
COLLEEN:
<i>Thank you.</i>

06:41.750 --> 06:43.125
-After you.
-Oh.

06:43.125 --> 06:44.625
I'm so glad you're
a let-the-lady-sit-first

06:44.625 --> 06:46.542
-kind of guy.
-Yeah, unfortunately,

06:46.542 --> 06:49.208
I am also a slide-my-hands-into
your-back-pockets kind of guy.

06:49.208 --> 06:50.709
I'll overlook it,
'cause you're very cute.

06:50.709 --> 06:52.000
Excuse me, sir?

06:52.000 --> 06:53.583
We're having trouble
starting your car.

06:53.583 --> 06:55.375
Oh, yeah, there's,
there's just a trick to it.

06:55.375 --> 06:56.417
-Okay.
-All right.

06:56.417 --> 06:59.041
I shall el return-o.

06:59.041 --> 07:00.917
