afford to fix it.

07:09.792 --> 07:12.041
You want to buy it?

07:12.041 --> 07:13.208
(thudding)

07:15.625 --> 07:17.125
It's broken.

07:22.375 --> 07:24.041
-Everything okay?
-Oh, yeah.

07:24.041 --> 07:27.333
Guy just didn't know
anything about cars--whoa,

07:27.333 --> 07:30.875
look at that wine list, huh,
there's so many of them.

07:30.875 --> 07:32.542
Sometimes I look at it,
I'm just, "Aah!"

07:32.542 --> 07:34.917
You know, ah, don't even
want any wine anymore.

07:34.917 --> 07:36.208
-There you go.
-Oh.

07:36.208 --> 07:37.417
So, I ordered
another one already?

07:37.417 --> 07:39.417
