07:55.375 --> 07:57.125
You're a good artist,
I'm terrible.

07:57.125 --> 07:59.041
-Nobody is a terrible artist.
-Okay.

07:59.041 --> 08:00.417
Pencils down.

08:00.417 --> 08:03.542
(breathing deeply)

08:03.542 --> 08:05.709
Some people
are terrible artists.

08:05.709 --> 08:07.125
That bad?

08:07.125 --> 08:09.625
-Oh, oh, let me.
-No, I got this.

08:09.625 --> 08:12.583
You may be the boss at work,
but I asked you out.

08:12.583 --> 08:14.750
I'm just gonna run this
up there, you know,

08:14.750 --> 08:17.417
