somewhere else tonight.

08:46.125 --> 08:48.709
-Okay, where?
-Mhm.

08:48.709 --> 08:50.458
At my wedding.

08:50.458 --> 08:52.083
I'm so sorry
I didn't tell you,

08:52.083 --> 08:56.041
but today is the day
I was going to marry Chad.

08:56.041 --> 08:57.250
-Oh.
-Yeah.

08:57.250 --> 08:58.542
